A clever way of achieving nice citations is to use bibliography items with custom labels, like this one:

[Johannesson & Lundstedt (2026)]	BIB:JL_custom
	Johannesson, Eric & Lundstedt, Anders (2026): Proof by weakened induction hypothesis.

Referring to it looks like this: [BIB:JL_custom].

Referring to the corresponding bibliography item in REFERENCES looks like this: [BIB:JL_custom_refs].

